    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly; the engine is incredibly smooth and responsive, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. Every feature and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
